pull.title: Remove straggling OpenSSL references from doc and build
pull.body:
Some doc and build cleanups following #17265.

I intentionally left the libssl-dev install in `gitian-win-signer.yml`, as it's necessary for the ossl signer.

repo.name: bitcoin
repo.description: Laanwj's Bitcoin Core fork - see README.md on "readme" branch

events.message: doc: Remove ssl as a required dependency from build-unix
build: remove libcrypto as internal dependency in libbitcoinconsensus.pc
test: remove lsan suppression for libcrypto
test: Remove libssl-dev packages from CI scripts
